{"tid":2349160,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"「女股神」Cathie Wood旗下方舟創新ETF 錄破記錄大額撤資","createTime":"2021-01-01T10:40:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T06:51:55.000Z","uid":66271,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"748e4976ac9eab22f21d8604112b1d5027c68c89","tid":2349160,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T10:40:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20201231/s00010/23ff7135c2d3e31bdfa3df046c6cd619.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20201231%2Fs00010%2F23ff7135c2d3e31bdfa3df046c6cd619.jpg&h=0e1ab4dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近期受追捧為「女股神」，更有稱為「連登契媽」的Cathie Wood，旗下旗艦基金「方舟創新 ETF」(ARK Innovation ETF)周二(29日)罕見出現投資者撤資，淨流出1.37億美元，是成立以來最多。<br />\n<br />\n該ETF今年12月4日成為全球最大主動型 ETF，總資產規模近176億美元，今次淨流出1.37億美元不僅是11月初以來首次單日淨流出，亦是按周計自2月以來首次淨流出。<br />\n<br />\n今年以來，該期金吸引到近94億美元資金投入，並投資於Tesla等股票，使該ETF的表現持續跑贏，或許是年結因素，部分投資者獲利離場。該ETF周二跌4.2%，而Cathie Wood另一基金ARK Genomic Revolution ETF (ARKG) 周二曾跌7.4%，但亦未見有大額淨流出。"},{"pid":"bb11b0a982e2943a3c13dd4e4c4258b65055fa2c","tid":2349160,"uid":149844,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T10:43:36.000Z","msg":"轉曬去all in Tesla<br />\n下年1000蚊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c137668d1609c176db765ee60fade997db5ac4c9","tid":2349160,"uid":108266,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T10:43:36.000Z","msg":"臭G應有此報"},{"pid":"12b2ecd5a85dd135522522d26d4a086c21f50895","tid":2349160,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T10:43:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c4d2e094af373a1b827a108b550b7d3e50df07c","tid":2349160,"uid":27319,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T10:44:36.000Z","msg":"麵麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj